  homepage http://prism54.org/newdrivers.html
  estimate 500
      desc 'prism54-firmare provides SoftMAC and FullMAC firmware for wireless NICs.

After installed rename the desired appropraite firmware image to:
/usr/lib/hotplug/firmware/isl3890

SoftMAC firmware versions:
» Version 2.4.6.0 for USB version 1 devices, using endpoints 0x02 and 0x82 (deprecated scheme)
» Version 2.5.6.0 for USB version 1 devices
» Version 2.5.8.0 for USB version 2 devices
» Version 2.7.0.0 for PCI devices

FullMAC firmware versions:
» Version 1.0.4.3 (for ISL3880 and ISL3890)
» Version 1.1.0.0 (for ISL3877)


Supported device list

